@zhangfeng114 It seems that your DolphinScheduler chart's appVersion is 1.3.5, but the used docker image is the latest (1.3.6). So either modify the `image.tag` in values.yaml to `1.3.5` (Or run `helm install dolphinscheduler . --set image.tag=1.3.5`), or just use the latest `1.3.6` DolphinScheduler chart.
There are a lot of optimizations related to docker and k8s in 1.3.6. Please refer to https://github.com/apache/dolphinscheduler/releases/tag/1.3.6
The official documentation: https://dolphinscheduler.apache.org/en-us/docs/1.3.6/user_doc/kubernetes-deployment.html

@4ss3g4f I am not sure what your question is about, maybe you need to provide a more specific description.
For example, did you encounter any problems during deployment or use?

You can find more helpful documents on this website.https://dolphinscheduler.apache.org
